      "exercise_id": "ex_ch01_metric_002",
      "version": "v1",
      "title": "计算精确率、召回率和 F1",
      "type": "coding",
      "chapter_id": "ch01",
      "related_node_id": "ml_performance_metrics",
      "assesses": ["ml_performance_metrics"],
      "also_assesses": ["ml_evaluation_methods"],
      "prerequisite_node_ids": ["ml_evaluation_methods"],
      "difficulty": 3,
      "estimated_minutes": 8,
      "cognitive_level": "apply",
      "assessment_focus": ["coding", "calculation"],
      "question": "补全 `precision_recall_f1` 函数，给定 TP、FP、FN，返回 precision、recall 和 F1。若分母为 0，本题约定对应指标为 0。",
      "starter_code": "def precision_recall_f1(tp, fp, fn):\n    # TODO: compute precision, recall, f1\n    pass\n",
      "options": [],
      "answer": {
        "reference_code": "def precision_recall_f1(tp, fp, fn):\n    precision = tp / (tp + fp) if tp + fp > 0 else 0\n    recall = tp / (tp + fn) if tp + fn > 0 else 0\n    f1 = 2 * precision * recall / (precision + recall) if precision + recall > 0 else 0\n    return precision, recall, f1\n",
        "explanation": "精确率衡量预测为正的样本中有多少是真的正，召回率衡量真实正样本中有多少被找回，F1 是二者的调和平均。"
      },
      "rubric": [
        {"criterion": "正确计算 precision", "score": 1},
        {"criterion": "正确计算 recall", "score": 1},
        {"criterion": "正确计算 F1", "score": 1},
        {"criterion": "处理分母为 0 的情况", "score": 1}
      ],
      "grading": {
        "method": "unit_test",
        "max_score": 4,
        "auto_gradable": true
